[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    113[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    114[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # --- Resource Names ---
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    115[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Fill these in with your actual resource names. The demo prints
