[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1108[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     The boto3 resource-level batch_writer() chunks into 25-item
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1109[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     batches and retries UnprocessedItems with exponential backoff
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1110[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     internally. The explicit chunking below is for clarity in a
